  "texts": [
    "Overall, the proposed DH-SNN model is simple but quite effective as evidenced by extensive experiments.",
    "An interesting topic in future work is to improve the model itself.",
    "The current modeling is based on the LIF neuron model, which is the simplest form of spiking neurons even though it is widely used.",
    "A possible way for model improvement is to build DH-SNNs based on more complicated spiking neuron models rather than the LIF one.",
    "For example, neuron models with more dendritic properties found in biological neurons seem promising."
  ],
